window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I was once a rejected wolf. Now, I'm the queen of the Fall Mountain Pack.</b></p> <p>I'm their alpha female. After escaping King Cenwyn and his court, I find myself back with my alphas, who are now my mates. I have everything I've ever wanted and more, but the gods have a different idea of freedom for me. Persephone's using the soul bond to connect to my mind and control it, but none of us know what she truly wants. King Cenwyn's armies are at our borders, and he isn't alone.</p> <p>The Levi are now an army controlled by an angry goddess, and if we aren't careful, she will destroy us all.</p> <p>We endure the fall and rise in the ashes.</p> <p>Fall Mountain Pack will not stay down for long. Wolves always bite backâ€¦</p> <p><i>This is a full-length reverse harem romance full of sexy alpha males, steamy scenes, a strong heroine, and a lot of sarcasm. Intended for mature listeners. Book five of eight.</i></p>"; 
